entries.journal_entry_description: Faeto has a couple of jobs to be done. Find Faeto and see what he wants.
entries.journal_entry_title: The Road of a Bounty Hunter
entries.task00_comm_message_text: It's time to let you loose on the galaxy. Talk to Faeto. He'll give you some jobs.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Boba mentioned someone named Faeto. Supposedly, this Faeto character has a couple of jobs. It would be a good idea to find him.
